<h1>Openbrokka Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 17 FEBRUARY 2026</p>

<p>Openbrokka ("we", "our", "us") operates a rental and apartment listing platform focused on Uganda. 
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application.</p>

<section>
<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>Account Information (Property Uploaders)</h3>
<ul>
<li>Name</li>
<li>Email address</li>
<li>Phone number</li>
<li>Authentication credentials (via Supabase Auth)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Property Content</h3>
<ul>
<li>Property descriptions</li>
<li>Photos</li>
<li>Videos</li>
<li>Location details</li>
<li>Rental price information</li>
</ul>

<h3>Communication Data</h3>
<ul>
<li>Phone numbers</li>
<li>Chat messages</li>
<li>Booking details</li>
</ul>

<h3>Device & Usage Data</h3>
<ul>
<li>Device type</li>
<li>App usage data</li>
<li>Crash logs</li>
<li>IP address</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2>2. Permissions We Use</h2>
<p><strong>Camera:</strong> Used to capture property photos and videos for listings.</p>
<p><strong>Storage:</strong> Used to upload and access property media files.</p>
<p>We do not access media without user action.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>
<ul>
<li>Create and manage accounts</li>
<li>Publish rental listings</li>
<li>Enable video feed browsing</li>
<li>Facilitate chats and bookings</li>
<li>Improve app performance</li>
<li>Ensure platform security</li>
<li>Prevent fraud and abuse</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We use Supabase for authentication, database storage, and secure backend services.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not sell personal data.</p>
<p>We may share information:</p>
<ul>
<li>Between users for booking communication</li>
<li>With service providers (Supabase infrastructure)</li>
<li>If required by law in Uganda</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
<p>We retain data as long as accounts remain active or as required by law. 
Users may request deletion at any time.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>7. Data Security</h2>
<p>We implement technical and administrative safeguards to protect user information. 
However, no system is completely secure.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>8. User Rights</h2>
<p>Users may request access, correction, or deletion of their data by contacting us.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>Openbrokka is not intended for children under 18. 
We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be reflected with a new effective date.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>11. Contact Information</h2>
<p>Email: ventureskrj@gmail.com</p>
<p>Country: Uganda</p>
</section>

</body>
